# papercast-studio · API key environment file.
#
# Each line is KEY=VALUE.  No quotes, no spaces around `=`. Lines
# starting with `#` are ignored.  Keep this file out of source control —
# the WebUI's 配置 page can write to it on your behalf.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LLM provider keys — fill in whichever ones you actually use.
# Settings → LLM Providers → 选 Provider → 填 API Key 也会写到这里。
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...
# DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-...
# MOONSHOT_API_KEY=sk-...
# ZHIPU_API_KEY=...

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TTS — MiniMax for voice synthesis & cloning.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# MINIMAX_API_KEY=eyJhbGciOi...

# 仅当克隆/合成报错 "token not match group" 时填写：
# 在 MiniMax 控制台 → 账户管理 → Group ID 复制粘贴。
# 2025 年中之后新签发的 token 不再把 group 编进 JWT，必须显式提供。
# MINIMAX_GROUP_ID=
